<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 16:19:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>币安为欧盟退出做准备，当地许可证悬而未决</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-16/binance-prepares-for-eu-exit-with-local-license-in-limbo</link><description>币安控股有限公司正准备停止在欧盟提供服务，因为获得欧盟运营许可证的最后期限即将到来，而且该加密货币交易所尚未获得希腊金融监管机构的批准。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ik0x1n3FXV_o/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 14:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-16/binance-prepares-for-eu-exit-with-local-license-in-limbo</guid></item><item><title>华尔街每天都在关注加密货币风格的交易</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-16/wall-street-stares-down-crypto-style-trading-all-day-every-day</link><description>&lt;p&gt;传统金融公司开始接受一系列资产的全天候交易，这种方式多年来一直扰乱加密货币的时间表。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/is5NKju56qKU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 15:17:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-16/wall-street-stares-down-crypto-style-trading-all-day-every-day</guid></item><item><title>将人工智能计算变成商品的竞赛刺激了新的加密货币热潮</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-16/race-to-turn-ai-compute-into-a-commodity-spurs-new-crypto-boom</link><description>伊森·维拉 (Ethan Vera) 认为卢克索科技 (Luxor Technology) 的未来是帮助比特币矿工买卖挖矿硬件。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iI1cnHB_y.QE/v8/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 13:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-16/race-to-turn-ai-compute-into-a-commodity-spurs-new-crypto-boom</guid></item><item><title>SpaceX 加密货币空头挤压导致价值短暂达到 3 万亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-16/spacex-crypto-short-squeeze-briefly-sends-value-to-3-trillion</link><description>周一美国股市收盘后不久，SpaceX 永续期货的轧空导致该公司在区块链市场上的隐含估值短暂升至 3 万亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4RtPOVJMyvI/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 10:20:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-16/spacex-crypto-short-squeeze-briefly-sends-value-to-3-trillion</guid></item><item><title>加密货币的真正牛仔：怀俄明州绳索 1 美元的稳定币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-16/wyoming-stablecoin-may-become-a-blueprint-or-cautionary-tale-for-other-states</link><description>&lt;p&gt;该州是黄石公园的所在地和富人的避难所，已成为美国第一个发行自己的加密货币的州。它的实验具有全国意义。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/inhS8z7aoFt0/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 09:30:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-16/wyoming-stablecoin-may-become-a-blueprint-or-cautionary-tale-for-other-states</guid></item><item><title>西德克萨斯州天然气四个月来首次升至零以上</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-15/west-texas-gas-rises-above-zero-for-first-time-in-four-months</link><description>周一，全球最大页岩油田的钻探人员在四个多月以来首次收到了生产天然气的报酬。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i37YwBTxj164/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 20:56:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-15/west-texas-gas-rises-above-zero-for-first-time-in-four-months</guid></item><item><title>美国与伊朗霍尔木兹协议达成后，比特币攀升至两周高点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-15/bitcoin-btc-rallies-to-two-week-high-after-us-iran-hormuz-deal</link><description>在美国和伊朗表示已达成协议结束敌对行动并重新开放霍尔木兹海峡后，比特币攀升至近两周来的最高水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iE2qC9NWzRdg/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 01:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-15/bitcoin-btc-rallies-to-two-week-high-after-us-iran-hormuz-deal</guid></item><item><title>SpaceX IPO 压力测试加密货币重塑股票的努力</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-15/spacex-ipo-stress-tests-crypto-s-bid-to-reinvent-stock-markets</link><description>多年来，加密货币公司一直认为，区块链技术可以在私营公司到达华尔街之前就为其创造市场。 SpaceX 提供了业界迄今为止最大规模的测试。结果好坏参半。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iL56vuq7Xnpc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 16:52:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-15/spacex-ipo-stress-tests-crypto-s-bid-to-reinvent-stock-markets</guid></item><item><title>Nuvei 同意以 27.5 亿美元的支付交易收购 Payoneer</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-15/nuvei-agrees-to-buy-payoneer-in-2-75-billion-payments-deal</link><description>Nuvei Corp. 已同意以约 27.5 亿美元收购 Payoneer Global Inc.，该交易将合并两家年处理量超过 5000 亿美元的北美支付公司。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iz4rNUG1b_TI/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 12:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-15/nuvei-agrees-to-buy-payoneer-in-2-75-billion-payments-deal</guid></item></channel></rss>